            <h1>The iPhone 17 Pro: Still Great, Still Overpriced.</h1>
        </div>

        <img src="placeholder.jpg" alt="iPhone 17 Pro large photo" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">

        <div class="score-box">
            <div>
                <h4>Overall Score</h4>
